# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# SpellCooldowns catalog for the Vanilla / Hardcore flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against SpellCooldowns.

Data_Vanilla\SpellCooldowns.lua
